The paper discusses networking challenges in Cloud Computing, which suggests that it belongs to the Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-category. Additionally, the paper also touches upon issues related to distributed computing (cs.DC), security (cs.CR), software engineering (cs.SE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), which are all relevant to Cloud Computing. Therefore, these sub-categories are also likely to be relevant to the paper.
